            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Il <rs key="#Bishops">vescovo</rs> di Lucca <persName ref="#people/213"
                            key="#Bishops">Pietro</persName> siede in giudizio hic <rs key="#Cities"
                            >civitate</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/4"
                            key="#Cities #Laubia/topia #Mother_churches #Bishops">Luca</placeName>
                        in <rs key="#Laubia/topia">laubia</rs> ipsius <orgName
                            key="#Mother_churches" ref="#juridical_persons/68"><rs
                                key="#Mother_churches">episcopatui</rs> Sancti Martini</orgName> con
                        il suddiacono Ghisalprando <rs key="#Missus_of_other_public_authorities"
                            >missus</rs> del <rs key="#Marquis/duke">marchese</rs>
                        <persName key="#Marquis/duke" ref="#people/137">Adalberto</persName>, gli
                        scabini Ghisalfridi, Benedetto, Adalperto, Leone e Cosperto; assistono, fra
                        gli altri, Fra(...), Flaiperto, <persName><name ref="Auripertus"
                                >Auriperto</name></persName>, Ghisolfo del <persName key="#Notary"
                            >fu <name ref="Georgius">Giorgio</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notaio</rs>, <persName><name ref="Gausfredus"
                                >Cosfridi</name></persName> di <persName><name ref="Adalbrandus"
                                >Adalprando</name></persName>, <persName><name ref="Leo"
                                >Leone</name></persName>, <persName><name
                                ref="Arderadus/Ardo de Marila">Arderado detto Ardo</name> de
                                <placeName ref="#places/60">Marila</placeName></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Teudebertus">Teuperto</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="David">Davide</name></persName>,
                                <persName><name ref="Benedictus">Benedetto</name></persName> di
                        Benedetto scabino, <persName>Erm(...)</persName>,
                            <persName>(...)malberto</persName> fratelli, <persName><name
                                ref="Christianus de Ovurno">Cristiano</name> de <placeName
                                ref="#places/2113">Ovurno</placeName></persName>, altro
                                <persName><name ref="Auripertus de Cumpito">Auriperto</name> de
                                <placeName ref="#places/721">Cumpito</placeName></persName>, Aufridi
                        chierico, Sicalfridi chierico, Adalfridi e Gheripaldo de Wamo, Wilimundo,
                        Gumperto chierico, Gumfridi, <persName><name ref="Ostribertus"
                                >Ostriperto</name></persName> (...). Si presenta da una parte il <rs
                            key="#Notary">notaio</rs> e <rs key="#Scabini">scabino</rs>
                        <persName key="#Notary #Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities #Scabini"
                                ><name ref="Petrus">Pietro</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities">advocatus</rs> dello stesso
                        vescovato, dall’altra i fratelli <persName><name ref="Ghisulfus"
                                >Ghisolfo</name></persName> e <persName><name ref="Tassilo"
                                >Tassilo</name></persName> del <persName>fu <name ref="Ostribertus"
                                >Ostriperto</name></persName>, in lite fra loro: secondo il notaio e
                        scabino la <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/1708"><rs
                                key="#Churches">chiesa</rs> di San Lorenzo</orgName> sita in loco et
                        finibus <placeName ref="#places/334" key="#Churches">Arsina</placeName> con
                        la metà delle sue dipendenze è una pertinenza della chiesa di (...) sito hic
                        Luca, qui est de suppotestatem del vescovato di San Martino; il fratelli non
                        contraddicono questa affermazione, ammettendo che la chiesa con la metà
                        delle sue dipendenze spettano ad pars <orgName key="#Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/246"><rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs> Sancti
                            Georgii</orgName> et predicti episcopatui Sancti Martini. Si chiede al
                            <rs key="#Writer #Notary">notaio</rs>
                        <persName key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Teuderandus"
                            >Teuderando</name></persName> la scrittura della notitia. <rs
                            key="#Witness">Testimoni</rs> sottoscrittori: <persName
                            key="#Witness #Missus_of_other_public_authorities #Subdeacons"><name
                                ref="Giselbrandus">Ghisalprando</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Subdeacons">subdiaconus</rs>, <persName
                            key="#Witness #Notary #Scabini"><name ref="Giselfredus"
                                >Ghisalfridi</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> et <rs key="#Scabini">schabinus</rs>,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Notary #Scabini"><name ref="Adalbertus"
                                >Adalperto</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> et <rs key="#Scabini">schabinus</rs>,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Notary #Scabini"><name ref="Leo"
                            >Leone</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> et <rs key="#Scabini">schabinus</rs>,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Notary #Scabini"><name ref="Gausbertus"
                                >Cosperto</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> et <rs key="#Scabini">schabinus</rs>,
                            <persName key="#Witness #Scabini"><name ref="Benedictus"
                                >Benedetto</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Scabini">schabinus</rs>, <persName key="#Witness"
                            ref="#people/150">Fraolmi</persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Flaipertus">Flaiperto</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Iohannes">Giovanni</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Roppaldus"
                            >Roppaldo</name></persName>, <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Ghisulfus">Ghisolfo</name></persName>.</ab>
                </div>
